title: Cook It Up v1.0
description:
Help young Oliver achieve his dream to become a Master Chef and step up to each culinary challenge to make your restaurant the best in town! 

You'll be chopping, slicing, frying, mixing and baking your way through the game, you'll even have to mop the floors! There are over 30 tasks to complete from mopping the floors to preparing complex signature dishes, so roll up your sleeves and get to work!

Key Features:

Experience the real feeling of cooking using the gesture-based actions.
A career spanning well over 30 levels working from kitchen hand to master chef.
Real recipes to create in-game and in real life!
Chop, fry, slice, blend, mop, cook your way to culinary uperstardom!
